            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">人民幣兌美元中間價報6.8616，下調34點；上日中間價6.8582，官方收盤價6.8185，夜盤收報6.8188。</p>\n</div>",
